<p>You just received your first vial of peptides, and you're staring at a tiny puck of powder wondering what to do next. Don't worry. Reconstitution is far simpler than it sounds once you see the process laid out.</p>

<p>This guide covers everything: what reconstitution is, the supplies you need, step-by-step instructions, dose math, and proper storage. You'll feel confident handling this within minutes.</p>

<div class="d">
