<h3>Bacteriostatic Water vs. Sterile Water</h3>

<p>This is a critical distinction. The wrong choice can ruin your vial or create a contamination risk.</p>

<div class="g2">
  <div class="cd ct">
    <div class="tg">Recommended</div>
    <h3>Bacteriostatic Water</h3>
